snippet.title: The game "Out of the Woods". The first walk in the forest.
snippet.description:
A short gameplay video with a walk through the world of the game "Title". Made specifically for GDWC 2022. A full teaser of the game will be presented by June 2023. You can get acquainted with the game on social media and Steam
